sailpoint.object

Class FilterRenderer

  • java.lang.Object
    • sailpoint.object.FilterRenderer
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Filter.FilterVisitor

    public class FilterRenderer
extends java.lang.Object
implements Filter.FilterVisitor
    A FilterVisitor that renders the filter as a SQL-like string. This is an alternative to the Filter.toString representation which is more Java-like. The intention is that this be used whenever you have to display a read-only summary of the filter, such as in approval work items. The syntax should more closely resemble what is shown in the modeler.
